Cthulu: a MEAN stack Single Page template
MongoDb, AngularJs, ExpressJs, Node.js, PassportJs, Mongoose, Zurb Foundation, Gulp, SASS, Angular ui-router, ejs, SweetAlerts

clone the repo
> git clone git@github.com:mikesankovich/Cthulu.git

>npm install

---------------------------
to install nodemon         |
> npm install -g nodemon   |
---------------------------

to compile SCSS into CSS, open a second tab in terminal and
>gulp

gulp will watch for changes in the SCSS and JS files and compile as you build

---------------------------
to install gulp            |
> npm install -g gulp      |
---------------------------

Make sure you have an instance of MongoDB running, then run gulp to fire up the server

Foundation Docs: http://foundation.zurb.com/docs/
SweetAlert Docs: http://oitozero.github.io/ngSweetAlert/#/home
ui-router Docs: https://github.com/angular-ui/ui-router
SASS basics: http://sass-lang.com/guide


directory paths:
Express routes: /routes/*.js
Template: views/index.ejs
Controller and state configuration: /public/javascripts/script.js
States: /public/views/*.ejs
SASS: /public/stylesheets/style.scss
mongoose schemas: /models/*.js
